name: King Inimicus the Twelfth
description:
Let's face it, Beldon Inimicus the Twelfth is obnoxious. He used to be a blacksmith before being fired for pushing (many) clients in the forge. He then was a manucurist for a while before becoming a crime lord, which naturally lead him to kill the previous king and take his place. Oh and by the way, he's the first of his lineag but wants to be called "The Twelfth" because it sounds posh. What a moron...
